               </fw>
            </tei:fw>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">― N. d. N. der junge <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_53756" ref="#person_14963"><surname>Feuchtwang</surname></rs>; <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_53757" ref="#person_19822"><forename>Heinis</forename></rs> Freund;― netter Junge.―</p>
